Updates on the confirmed cases(as of 1 Feb.) of novel Coronavirus in Republic of Korea 
- Contacts are under epidemiological investigation - 
 
○ As of 1 February, 2020, there have been 371 Patient Under Investigation(PUIs) and 12 confirmed cases in total, 289 cases released from isolation, and 70 cases currently being tested. 




 

